    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Slumbering Woods（沉睡之森）</i>是一款温馨、手绘风格的探索与种植蘑菇冒险游戏，背景设定在一个从遥远气候灾难中逐渐恢复的世界中。你将扮演一位旅行草药师，努力拯救一个被沼泽淹没的偏远村庄，并重建这个四分五裂的社区。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索的过程中，你将发现古老传说、在旧书中找到被遗忘的制作配方，并逐步揭开村庄及其周边的神秘面纱。你可以自定义废弃的小屋，与村民建立关系，并做出影响生态系统恢复的关键选择。借助灵活的昼夜循环系统，由你自己掌控游戏节奏——白天劳作，傍晚社交，在日记中记录进展，一点点让村庄重现生机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>种植漂浮蘑菇岛，塑造地貌。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/ff1b70044191e0c745a969604c1c06fa.poster.avif?t=1772242227\" width=800 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/ff1b70044191e0c745a969604c1c06fa.webm?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/ff1b70044191e0c745a969604c1c06fa.mp4?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>夜晚与村民交流互动。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/d664369f3f382a73b6b1edee8ff30e30.poster.avif?t=1772242227\" width=800 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/d664369f3f382a73b6b1edee8ff30e30.webm?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/d664369f3f382a73b6b1edee8ff30e30.mp4?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>种植蘑菇以解谜并清理土地。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/7a1d6aed72ee053d8dc7cb78e4664682.poster.avif?t=1772242227\" width=800 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/7a1d6aed72ee053d8dc7cb78e4664682.webm?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/7a1d6aed72ee053d8dc7cb78e4664682.mp4?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集资源，在村中能工巧匠的帮助下制作工具和材料。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/257219537b3d67d5d853770d399e30d2.avif?t=1772242227\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>灵活的昼夜循环。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可在自己准备好时推进时间段。白天可用于探索与制作。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/3499edbbaca02c5ab238c6f5de85effc.poster.avif?t=1772242227\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/3499edbbaca02c5ab238c6f5de85effc.webm?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/3499edbbaca02c5ab238c6f5de85effc.mp4?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>探索危险却美丽的蘑菇荒野。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/49a58f49f1b45b1345c8e5fc8da86f66.poster.avif?t=1772242227\" width=640 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/49a58f49f1b45b1345c8e5fc8da86f66.webm?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/49a58f49f1b45b1345c8e5fc8da86f66.mp4?t=1772242227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发现隐藏的蘑菇并学习其种植方法。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3243350/extras/46cc0cc824407b8ec31e1e104a277a22.avif?t=1772242227\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
